{"tid":1662463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致陳彥霖的真朋友及Roommate","createTime":"2019-10-18T18:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T16:32:31.000Z","uid":253170,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8c76a088b62cbe4e14aa156870c97a6cf31c561a","tid":1662463,"uid":253170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:47:03.000Z","msg":"首先希望你地認清現實同自己處境<br />\n<br />\n1. 陳彥霖自殺或被殺，短期內很難真相大白。<br />\n<br />\n2. 不論陳彥霖是否自殺，警方於事件處事手法令人懷疑背後有所隱瞞。<br />\n<br />\n3. 據以中共一貫處事手法所推測，會對可能知道真相既人進行威逼滅聲。<br />\n<br />\n4. 無心令各位受驚，但請認清一點:<br />\n事以至此，你們無法置身事外，不論公義方面或自身安全方面。<br />\n<br />\n5. 事態已經發展到不論&rdquo;朋友&rdquo;爆料、VTC CCTV、&rdquo;親母&rdquo;訪問都無法令我地相信陳彥霖的死是單純的自殺，除非有更強力的物證或人證，否則真相會慢慢石沉大海。<br />\n<br />\n7. 不希望有人再為此事受到傷害，因此你們的自身個人安全是首要考慮因素。<br />\n <br />\n若果你們手上有重要的證據或真相，<br />\n如能夠證實陳母說謊，<br />\n或CCTV中女子是否陳本人，<br />\n陳與家人之關係，<br />\n幾時入女童院，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請不要再於網上匿名爆料。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">原因一: 匿名爆料無法令人相信 (太多假消息)<br />\n原因二: 現時連匿名都未必確保到安全</span><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">建議一: </span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">主動聯絡立法會議員，尋求支援及報料</span>，再由議員決定是否公開，或者舉行聯合匿名記招。<br />\n由議員公開可以增加公信力，同時有議員睇住狗未必敢咬人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">建議二: </span><br />\n做定心理準備會有狗上門，定期向身邊人<span style=\"color: blue;\">報平安</span>。<br />\n <br />\n另外我特別擔心既係<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">陳彥霖既roommate(如果有)</span></span>，我唔知狗上左黎搜屋未，但肯定既係狗會視你為一個極大既不確定因素，你既處境的確比其他人更危險。<br />\n由於外界對Roommate係咪真實存在都未知，你被消失左亦都唔會有人知。<br />\n我認為最能夠保護你既係傳媒同社會既關注度，所以建議你最起碼比議員知道你既存在。"},{"pid":"76c9148b43a7bc3180080f5dce9d56e2d8e9f33c","tid":1662463,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:47:30.000Z","msg":"10.20見<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fcRaCh8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfcRaCh8.png&h=6a019475&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c04a478580d7a36ffe28a3141d965bceadd5adbb","tid":1662463,"uid":288830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:48:13.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/enANcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/enANcS</a><br />\n<br />\n幫推！"},{"pid":"192bd2626685a25a9a4d79b27613d8ff42c97918","tid":1662463,"uid":84936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:56:35.000Z","msg":"推到佢地睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ae0ce90748b3ed1091928350cf44477d060b92","tid":1662463,"uid":84936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:56:52.000Z","msg":"10.20見"},{"pid":"0721733016f83073f919164150d14394b002f5d3","tid":1662463,"uid":84936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:57:05.000Z","msg":"10.20！"},{"pid":"3c09e45f1b899fb2c9156c8d9b6e8a952abe9c64","tid":1662463,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:11:27.000Z","msg":"【日常文宣】[推爆佢]本土國際戰線&mdash;Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1662234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1662234</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"12f77c82a880ec56ca6e97badb24f2e839925b59","tid":1662463,"uid":83072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T21:17:45.000Z","msg":"試下唔好半夜開post."},{"pid":"2ca8fbeebedce19371c84ff80682a6d90597d4ad","tid":1662463,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T21:18:36.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"f933317554967221ca2995a45e7ec58cf7f6b097","tid":1662463,"uid":161709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T23:06:37.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b3530c827835976c352ac1001e9e1d47276d39b","tid":1662463,"uid":50290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T23:09:04.000Z","msg":"最新彥霖案第一身內幕，驚人發展。好爆，唔係網傳資料。有3parts<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/N1m80bHF-Wk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FN1m80bHF-Wk&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9q9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=9feeaea6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/N1m80bHF-Wk</a>"},{"pid":"6c36f301d9b23d73c401ab5eb2cb261c470104a7","tid":1662463,"uid":275750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T23:13:36.000Z","msg":"可能已經消失咗"},{"pid":"72b94b1b50b59790b16ec1dc280e6a5f8a0a66b5","tid":1662463,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:27:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e073e9053a436ce314d724588bf5dbc57b505ccc","tid":1662463,"uid":276758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:35:14.000Z","msg":"仲有彥霖係監獄既男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢應該最清楚自己女朋友會唔會自殺.."},{"pid":"b7cf6a3296f7b2a7f2fbc70b3d74fe069c1f672c","tid":1662463,"uid":253170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:47:21.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"732fdbc40e7bd2e3a6ccbce66b40641283e9b3f4","tid":1662463,"ui